Create automation test case for this website:  https://www.saucedemo.com/:
1.	Have a successful login.
2.	Have an unsuccessful login.
3.	Add items (you should have two items that are shown in the cart element) to the cart.
4.	Checkout on added items in the cart (those items must be different from №3)
5.	For additional points: check what bugs does the problem users have. (login with them)
Make a test with one of the problem users account. (That means a test that will fail.)


Scoring:
//Todo 1.	Project is in Page Object Model  - 10 points
//Todo 2.	Проекта поддържа два браузъра - хром и файрфокс - 10 points
//Todo 3.	Избор на браузър и урл се подават като конфигурация - 10 points
4.	Every driver is closed after test completion - 10 points
5.	Every test is in separate class - 10 points
6.	Паралелно изпълнение на тестове (поне два паралелни) - 10 points
//Todo 7.	Тестови данни се пазаят (и четат от) csv file - 10 points
8.	Implicit wait is used - 10 points
9.	Explicit wait is used - 10 points
10.	Assert is used- 10 points
